   the band head using estimated spectroscopic constants. These data
   provide a set of much improved equilibrium vibrational and rotational
   constants for the $A\ ^6\Sigma^+$ state. An accurate description of the
   A-X transition has been obtained using a multireference configuration
   interaction approach. The inclusion of both scalar relativity and Cr
